'''挪威巨蟹'''（[[學名|學名]]''Lithodes maja''）是一種分佈在[[歐洲|歐洲]]及[[北美洲|北美洲]]寒冷水域的[[皇帝蟹|皇帝蟹]]。在整個[[挪威|挪威]]沿岸<ref name="Telnes">{{cite web|url=http://www.seawater.no/fauna/Leddyr/maja.htm|title=Deepsea king crab|author=K. Telnes|accessdate=2007-08-16|publisher=seawater.no|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070703233804/http://www.seawater.no/fauna/Leddyr/maja.htm|archivedate=2007-07-03}}</ref>、[[不列顛群島|不列顛群島]]、[[法羅群島|法羅群島]]、[[冰島|冰島]]、[[斯瓦爾巴群島|斯瓦爾巴群島]]及[[格陵蘭|格陵蘭]]東南部都可以發現它們的蹤影。<ref name="Troms"/>在[[加拿大|加拿大]]，它們則分佈在[[紐芬蘭-拉布拉多|紐芬蘭-拉布拉多]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://canadianbiodiversity.mcgill.ca/english/species/crustaceans/crustaceanpages/lit_maj.htm|title=Stone crab, ''Lithodes maja''|publisher=McGill University|work=Canada's Species|accessdate=2007-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170314075333/http://canadianbiodiversity.mcgill.ca/english/species/crustaceans/crustaceanpages/lit_maj.htm|archive-date=2017-03-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

挪威巨蟹的甲殼差不多呈圓形，闊約13-14厘米。<ref name="Telnes"/>整體呈褐色或橙色，表面有大刺覆蓋。它們棲息在柔軟及堅硬的海床，由水深幾米至800米不等。<ref name="Troms"/><ref name="Telnes"/>它們就像大部份皇帝蟹般，雌蟹是不對稱的，左邊[[腹部|腹部]]較右邊大，但也有一些是相反的。<ref>{{cite journal en|author=S. D. Zaklan|year=2000|title=A case of reversed asymmetry in ''Lithodes maja'' (Linnaeus, 1758) (Decapoda, Anomura, Lithodidae)|journal=Crustaceana|volume=73|issue=8|pages=1019–1022|doi=10.1163/156854000504949}}</ref>

挪威巨蟹的產卵率很低，故其數量因而受限，並不適合商業用途。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.fishaq.gov.nl.ca/fdp/projectreports/fdp_84.pdf|format=PDF|title=Northern stone crab (''Lithodes maja'') exploratory fishing|publisher=Government of Newfoundland and Labrador|year=2000|access-date=2010-05-10|archive-date=2007-05-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070503191813/http://www.fishaq.gov.nl.ca/fdp/projectreports/fdp_84.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

